data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort & style in this one story, 4-bedroom, 2-bath brick home nestled on a peaceful cul-de-sac. Step inside to find wood laminate flooring throughout the main living area, creating a warm & inviting atmosphere. The open concept design seamlessly connects the kitchen to the living room, making it ideal for gatherings. The heart of the home features a large island with a breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances, & a convenient walk-in pantry. The primary suite is a true retreat, boasting a spacious walk-in closet & an ensuite bathroom with double sinks, a jetted tub, and a separate shower. Outside, a generously sized backyard awaits, providing endless opportunities for outdoor enjoyment. Relax on the covered back patio & savor the tranquility of your private oasis. This home also offers a water softener system and tankless water heater.  NE facing & zoned to Cy-Fair ISD! Close to shopping, restaurants & more! FRIDGE, WASHER, DRYER,& TV INCLUDED!
